<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ نُوح<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٠:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {فَقُلْتُ اسْتَغْفِرُوا رَبَّكُمْ إِنَّهُ كَانَ غَفَّارًا <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> يُرْسِلِ السَّمَاءَ عَلَيْكُمْ مِدْرَارًا <span class="c2">(١١)</span>} <span class="c4">[نوح: ١٠ - ١١]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{مِدْرَارًا}</span>: <span class="c2">«يَتْبَعُ بَعْضُهَا بَعْضًا»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>